OL,3,CLisa Nandy says she's prepared to take
OL,4,Con 'cultures of silence'
OL,6,FCulture Secretary Lisa Nandy said she
OL,7,Fis prepared to take action if
OL,8,F"cultures of silence and issues being
OL,9,Fswept under the rug" are not addressed
OL,10,Fby the media industry, following
OL,11,Fmisconduct claims against TV
OL,12,Fpresenter, Gregg Wallace.
OL,14,FAt the Culture, Media and Sport
OL,15,FCommittee on Tuesday, Ms Nandy made
OL,16,Freference to the recent allegations of
OL,17,Finappropriate behaviour by MasterChef
OL,18,Fhost and failure of complaint
OL,19,Fprocedures.
