OL,3,CLisa Nandy says she's prepared to take
OL,4,Con 'cultures of silence'
OL,6,F"We're seeing too many of these
OL,7,Fcultures of silence and issues being
OL,8,Fswept under the rug."
OL,10,FThe Culture Secretary said she will be
OL,11,Fmeeting with the Creative Industries
OL,12,FIndependent Standards Authority, an
OL,13,Findependent body tackling bullying and
OL,14,Fharassment in the sector, on Wednesday.
OL,16,FShe added: "They think, and I
OL,17,Finstinctively think, that it is better
OL,18,Fif the industry grips this, but if
OL,19,Fthey don't I will be prepared to take
OL,20,Ffurther action."
